'''2013年12月伏尔加格勒爆炸事件'''是指2013年12月29日和30日在[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]][[南部聯邦管區|南部聯邦管區]][[伏尔加格勒州|伏尔加格勒州]][[伏尔加格勒|伏尔加格勒市]]发生的两起独立[[自杀式袭击|自杀式袭击]]事件。共造成包括肇事者在内的34人死亡。<ref>[http://www.apdnews.com/photo/58160.html 俄接连发生两起恐袭] {{Wayback|url=http://www.apdnews.com/photo/58160.html |date=20131231205043 }}，亚太日报，2013年12月31日</ref><ref name="311213TDIU">{{Cite web | url = http://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/184629.html | title = Death toll from Volgograd blasts rises to 34 | publisher = [[Interfax-Ukraine|Interfax-Ukraine]] | date = 2013-12-31 | accessdate = 2013-12-31 | archive-date = 2018-10-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181005043843/https://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/184629.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>此前的10月21日该城市曾发生了[[2013年伏尔加格勒公共汽车爆炸事件|公共汽车爆炸事件]]。

==12月29日火车站爆炸==
2013年12月29日在[[伏爾加格勒1號站|伏爾加格勒1號站]]发生自杀式爆炸袭击，共造成至少18人死亡，44人受伤，其中38人入院治疗<ref name="video"/>。袭击发生在[[莫斯科时间|莫斯科时间]]12:45<ref name=lenta>{{cite news|url=http://lenta.ru/news/2013/12/29/explos/|title=Названа мощность взрыва на волгоградском вокзале|date=2013-12-29|work=Lenta|language=ru|accessdate=2013-12-29|archive-date=2016-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807043851/https://lenta.ru/news/2013/12/29/explos/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，一名自杀式袭击者在[[伏爾加格勒1號站|伏爾加格勒1號站]]靠近车站入口金属探测器处引爆了相当于{{convert|10|kg}}TNT炸药的炸弹背心<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/world/female-suicide-bomber-attack-in-volgograd-russia-as-sochi-winter-olympics-approach-20131229-hv749.html|work=[[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]]|accessdate=2013-12-29|date=2013-12-29|title=Female suicide bomber attack in Volgograd, Russia, as Sochi Winter Olympics approach|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929082304/https://www.smh.com.au/world/female-suicide-bomber-attack-in-volgograd-russia-as-sochi-winter-olympics-approach-20131229-hv749.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，附近监控记录下了事发过程。<ref name=video>{{cite news|url=http://rt.com/news/volgograd-blast-victims-russia-937/|title=Suicide bombing kills at least 17 in Russia's Volgograd (video)|date=2013-12-29|work=[[RT_(TV_network)|RT]]|accessdate=2013-12-30|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111194556/https://www.rt.com/news/volgograd-blast-victims-russia-937/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

最初一些报道认为爆炸由一名女性自杀式袭击者所为。<ref name=RT/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/12/29/us-russia-blast-idUSBRE9BS02S20131229|title=Female suicide bomber kills 13 at Russian train station|work=Reuters|accessdate=2013-12-29|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924192052/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/12/29/us-russia-blast-idUSBRE9BS02S20131229|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/12/29/world/europe/russia-train-station-explosion/index.html?hpt=hp_t1|title=14 die as second bomb attack in 2 months strikes Russian city|work=CNN|accessdate=2013-12-29|archive-date=2016-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104162243/http://www.cnn.com/2013/12/29/world/europe/russia-train-station-explosion/index.html?hpt=hp_t1|dead-url=no}}</ref>她们被称作[[黑寡妇_(车臣)|黑寡妇]]，当局曾称袭击者为Oksana Aslanova。<ref name=RT>{{cite web|url=http://rt.com/news/volgograd-suicide-bombing-updates-940/|title=Volgograd railway station blast|date=2013-12-29|accessdate=2013-12-29|work=[[RT_(TV_network)|RT]]|archive-date=2013-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230021005/http://rt.com/news/volgograd-suicide-bombing-updates-940/|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而后来没有确定袭击者身份<ref name=bbc1>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-25541019|title='Suicide bomber' hits Russia's Volgograd train station|date=2013-12-29|accessdate=2013-12-29|work=BBC News|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112011915/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-25541019|dead-url=no}}</ref>，有一些新闻机构称袭击者是一名男性。<ref name=Guard>{{cite news|last=Ragozin|first=Leonid|title=Volgograd train station rocked by suicide bombing|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/dec/29/volgograd-train-station-suicide-bombing|accessdate=2013-12-29|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2013-12-29|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112022150/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/dec/29/volgograd-train-station-suicide-bombing|dead-url=no}}</ref>没有任何组织声称对这次袭击负责。<ref name=Reuters131231>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/12/31/us-russia-blast-idUSBRE9BU05E20131231|newspaper=Reuters|title=Russian police round up dozens after suicide bombings|date=2013-12-31|author=Sergei Karpov|accessdate=2013-12-31|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924192122/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/12/31/us-russia-blast-idUSBRE9BU05E20131231|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[俄罗斯总统|俄罗斯总统]][[普京|普京]]下令将重伤员空运到莫斯科治疗。<ref name="bbc1" />

==12月30日无轨电车爆炸==

第二次袭击发生在12月30日上午约7:30的伏尔加格勒的{{tsl|ru|Дзержинский район (Волгоград)|捷尔任斯基区 (伏尔加格勒)|捷尔任斯基区}}，目标是连接郊区和市中心的一辆15路[[无轨电车|无轨电车]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rt.com/news/russia-volgograd-trolley-blast-957/|title=Consecutive Volgograd suicide bombing kills at least 14|work=RT|date=2013-12-30|accessdate=2013-12-30|archive-date=2020-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213101416/https://www.rt.com/news/russia-volgograd-trolley-blast-957/|dead-url=no}}</ref>从目击者拍摄的照片来看爆炸发生在无轨电车后面。<ref name=bbctrolley>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-25546477|title=Volgograd blasts: New deadly explosion hits Russian city|work=BBC News|accessdate=2013-12-30|date=2013-12-30|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112004641/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-25546477|dead-url=no}}</ref>有16人在爆炸中死亡，41人受伤，其中27人被送进医院。<ref name=graphic>{{cite web|url=http://rt.com/news/russia-volgograd-trolley-blast-957/|title=Volgograd suicide bombing kills at least 14 (photos, graphic video)|work=RT|date=2013-12-30|accessdate=2013-12-30|archive-date=2020-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213101416/https://www.rt.com/news/russia-volgograd-trolley-blast-957/|dead-url=no}}</ref>男性袭击者的遗体被找到并将进行基因检测。<ref name=bbctrolley/>

